abstract_ssm: The collection includes two photographs showing houses on Beverley Road in Brooklyn; a photograph showing two unidentified children standing outside of a large house; a photograph of a boy on roller skates holding a hockey stick and standing in front of a car on a sidewalk; a photograph of two unidentified adults standing on a residential sidewalk in front a parked car; and one 8" x 10" print of an unidentified woman sitting on a bench located along the boardwalk in front of the Brighton Hotel in Brighton Beach.
